---
title: Pineapple-Apricot Pork Chops with Rosemary-Parmesan Potatoes and Snap Peas
description: Fresh pineapple and apricot spread make for the perfect sweet and savoury sauce to go with pork chops! Parboiled potatoes are finished in the pan with rosemary and a sprinkle of Parmesan for the ultimate fluffy on the inside, crispy on the outside texture and maximum flavour.
